---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The World"
  description="An original fantasy world by Alexandros Emmanouilidis — built from scratch, with its own mythology, geography, magic system, and a novel in progress here."
>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container--narrow">

      <a href="/portfolio" class="back-link">&larr; Portfolio</a>

      <div class="project-header">
        <span class="item-tag">Creative · Worldbuilding · Work in progress</span>
        <h1>The World</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="project-body">
        <p class="project-lead">
          An original fantasy world — not adapted from existing fiction, not borrowing
          established settings. Built from scratch, with the intention of writing a full
          novel set inside it. Possibly many.
        </p>

        <p>
          The mythology, geography, history, magic system, species, and internal logic of
          this world are being developed in parallel with the fiction it will eventually
          contain. Everything is made to be consistent — the rules of the Dream (the world's
          ambient magical force), the way societies formed around access to it, the
          geography that shaped those societies, and the history that resulted.
        </p>

        <p>
          <a href="/portfolio/blind-tracks">Blind Tracks</a> is the first published piece
          set here. Taren, the Null who follows blind tracks through a crimson storm, exists
          inside this world. The story was written to test whether the internal logic held
          under narrative pressure. It did.
        </p>

        <p>
          The project moves slowly and deliberately. That's by design — a world built in
          a weekend collapses under its own weight. This one is being built to last.
        </p>

        <div class="wip-note">
          <span class="wip-label">Status</span>
          <p>Ongoing. The world is under active development. The novel is in early stages.
          Updates will appear here when there's something worth sharing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <div class="project-footer">
        <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn--ghost">&larr; Back to portfolio</a>
        <a href="/portfolio/blind-tracks" class="btn btn--ghost">Read Blind Tracks &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .back-link:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .project-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .item-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  h1 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .project-body {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .project-lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 58ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .project-body p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .wip-note {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }

  .wip-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .wip-note p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 55ch;
  }

  .project-footer {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
